        "detailedDescription_md": "&quot;A Scheme to Provide Assistance for Building E-Market Facilities in Market Committees&quot; introduced by the Agriculture, Farmers Welfare and Cooperation Department, Gujarat, aims to support market committees to set up e-market facilities, enhancing transparency and efficiency in agricultural marketing across the state.\n",
